fem.components

Class AbstractElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.model.NamedObject
      • fem.components.AbstractElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IElement, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, INamedObject, IStreamable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstantStrainTriangle, PlaneQuad4Iso, Quad4Iso, Triangle

    public abstract class AbstractElement
extends NamedObject
implements IElement
    This class is abstract with super class IElement and is the parent class of all finite elements. Class contains generic get and set methods required for implementing a finite element into the FemModel.
    See Also:
